reviewText: I enjoyed it. I plan to watch it again and again because, for me, I see details that I didn't notice the first time. Great history lesson as well.
YES, THIS IS IT. A CHARM OF A REEL. IT MAKES YOU FEEL THE REAL SEAL OF APPROVAL FROM A SISTER WHO KNOWS THE LINKAGE TO HER CUBAN SOUL. CAN'T TOUCH OR DON'T TOUCH THE PUFF.
